citation: Motor Accidents (Liabilities and Compensation) Amendment Act 2007 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Motor Accidents (Liabilities and Compensation) Amendment Act 2007 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Motor Accidents (Liabilities and Compensation) Amendment Act 2007 has been repealed by Schedule 1 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
